message: Hello future player! My strategy was to use the 'stove' tool on all raw ingredients first. For any ingredient that didn't gain value (remained 0) after using the 'stove' (often grains like bread, rice, corn, tortilla, wheat), use the 'water' tool on it next, which usually brings its value to 20. Then, combine two of the stove-benefited ingredients (value 20 each) to create a new item (value 60). Finally, combine this new item (value 60) with one of the water-treated ingredients (value 20) to reach the maximum value of 100. Once you reach 100, submit immediately, as further combinations can lower your score or yield nothing. Good luck!
